00:39:49,036 --> 00:39:52,080
Ouch. So fierce.

540
00:39:52,080 --> 00:39:55,600
How can a beautiful girl like you be this fierce to me?

541
00:39:55,600 --> 00:39:57,700
Ah. I'll stop teasing you.

542
00:39:57,700 --> 00:40:00,810
I'll have a cocoa smoothie.

543
00:40:00,810 --> 00:40:02,570
Extra dark.

544
00:40:02,570 --> 00:40:05,940
No cream, no sugar. Don't put anything in it.

545
00:40:05,940 --> 00:40:07,100
No sweetener at all.

546
00:40:07,100 --> 00:40:10,472
I repeat, no sweetener at all. Strong and thick.

547
00:40:10,473 --> 00:40:14,209
I want something that can make you drop dead after a sip.

548
00:40:14,209 --> 00:40:16,770
Are you joking?

549
00:40:16,770 --> 00:40:19,767
I order this for real!

550
00:40:20,306 --> 00:40:23,834
Or... can you not do it?

551
00:40:23,834 --> 00:40:24,731
I can.

552
00:40:24,731 --> 00:40:28,522
Ouch. Such a dry speaker.

553
00:40:28,522 --> 00:40:31,401
I'll make a complaint to the shop owner.

554
00:40:31,401 --> 00:40:33,189
Hey, Beautiful.

555
00:40:33,189 --> 00:40:36,414
For another cup, I need a strawberry smoothie.

556
00:40:36,414 --> 00:40:39,880
This one, I need it sweet.

557
00:40:39,880 --> 00:40:43,672
As sweet as your face.

558
00:40:43,672 --> 00:40:47,281
Yes. Very sweet, right?

559
00:40:47,281 --> 00:40:48,579
Asshole Pond.

560
00:40:48,579 --> 00:40:50,786
What takes you so long to buy a drink?

561
00:40:50,786 --> 00:40:53,244
I dropped by the dorm already.

562
00:40:53,244 --> 00:40:54,698
Right.

563
00:40:54,698 --> 00:40:56,536
They're kind of very slow here.

564
00:40:56,537 --> 00:40:57,877
What?

565
00:41:04,511 --> 00:41:08,054
Hey, Koon-Chai Pete.

566
00:41:08,054 --> 00:41:10,469
What brought you here?

567
00:41:10,469 --> 00:41:13,060
Right. What about that scumbag?

568
00:41:13,060 --> 00:41:15,058
Is he still coming to bother you?

569
00:41:15,059 --> 00:41:16,389
He's been quiet.

570
00:41:16,390 --> 00:41:18,068
Thank you very much, Ae.

571
00:41:18,068 --> 00:41:19,690
What's that for?

572
00:41:19,690 --> 00:41:22,487
You always say "Thank you" every time we meet.

573
00:41:22,487 --> 00:41:25,191
Thank you for the other day.

574
00:41:25,191 --> 00:41:27,284
Enough talking about that.

575
00:41:27,284 --> 00:41:28,786
Oh.

576
00:41:29,521 --> 00:41:31,406
Did you talk to your mom?

577
00:41:31,406 --> 00:41:33,040
I did.

578
00:41:33,040 --> 00:41:35,840
Hey, Ae. Who's this?

579
00:41:35,840 --> 00:41:37,552
Your friend?

580
00:41:39,123 --> 00:41:41,593
- Nice to meet you.
- Hello, hello.

581
00:41:41,593 --> 00:41:43,323
Never seen you around here.

582
00:41:43,323 --> 00:41:46,153
- From the soccer team?
- How nosy, Ai'Pond!

583
00:41:46,153 --> 00:41:48,480
That's kind of all over my face.

584
00:41:49,640 --> 00:41:52,773
Right. What are you doing here?

585
00:41:52,773 --> 00:41:55,660
Isn't there a canteen in the International Building?

586
00:41:55,660 --> 00:42:00,239
I couldn't find a parking spot, so I had to park near here.

587
00:42:00,239 --> 00:42:02,532
Wow, that's quite far.

588
00:42:02,533 --> 00:42:04,510
One cocoa smoothie.

589
00:42:12,950 --> 00:42:15,220
Here. It's yours.

590
00:42:15,220 --> 00:42:17,733
- Ae'Khrab—
- Shh!

591
00:42:22,265 --> 00:42:25,251
You're the one who ordered this. You can have the first sip.

592
00:42:25,251 --> 00:42:28,998
Come on. We're good friends.

593
00:42:28,998 --> 00:42:30,341
This is just a drink.

594
00:42:30,342 --> 00:42:32,683
Don't mind me. You go ahead.

595
00:42:32,683 --> 00:42:34,683
I said, drink it.

596
00:42:39,182 --> 00:42:42,000
This is good, shitty good.

597
00:42:47,880 --> 00:42:49,405
It's actually good.

598
00:42:49,406 --> 00:42:53,039
What? It's that bitter and you say it's good?

599
00:42:53,039 --> 00:42:56,527
I thought she put wormwood instead of sugar.

600
00:42:59,819 --> 00:43:02,730
Right, Pete. Have you had lunch yet?

601
00:43:02,730 --> 00:43:05,749
Here. A sandwich.

602
00:43:05,749 --> 00:43:08,719
For me, that's just an appetizer.

603
00:43:08,720 --> 00:43:10,968
It takes ten minutes to burn those calories.

604
00:43:10,969 --> 00:43:13,442
Want to go? I'll treat you to a real lunch.

605
00:43:13,443 --> 00:43:16,913
I don't want to bother you. You're with your friend.

606
00:43:17,946 --> 00:43:19,750
Ai'Pond?

607
00:43:19,750 --> 00:43:22,980
Chat with him for a few minutes and you'll become friends.

608
00:43:23,014 --> 00:43:25,163
- Want to go?
- Sure.

609
00:43:25,164 --> 00:43:27,148
What on earth brought you two together?

610
00:43:27,148 --> 00:43:29,593
Grassroots Shorty and

611
00:43:29,593 --> 00:43:32,143
Koon-Chai meeting each other.

612
00:43:32,143 --> 00:43:34,331
The Sa-tor-berry smoothie is here.

613
00:43:34,332 --> 00:43:35,801
(T/N : Sa-tor: Slang for "liar")

614
00:43:35,801 --> 00:43:38,928
Thank you. I can drink something sweet now.

615
00:43:41,634 --> 00:43:43,578
This one's way too sweet!

616
00:43:43,578 --> 00:43:45,361
Didn't you order a very sweet one?

617
00:43:45,362 --> 00:43:47,447
So, here you are.

618
00:43:47,447 --> 00:43:50,154
After drinking, the sugar will reach your brain cells.

619
00:43:50,154 --> 00:43:54,082
After that, you'll know what to say and what not to say.

620
00:43:54,603 --> 00:43:56,813
Thank you very much.

621
00:44:00,338 --> 00:44:03,962
- Ai'Pete, let's go.
- Sure.

622
00:44:08,560 --> 00:44:10,739
Want to have lunch with me, Beautiful?

623
00:44:10,739 --> 00:44:13,040
Reserve your mouth for eating only.

624
00:44:13,920 --> 00:44:17,031
Can I reserve it for eating with you?

625
00:44:17,031 --> 00:44:19,088
Okay. I'll go.

626
00:44:19,088 --> 00:44:22,005
I'll return it. It's too sweet to drink.

627
00:44:22,901 --> 00:44:24,534
- How much?
- 100 baht.

628
00:44:24,535 --> 00:44:26,722
What? So expensive.

629
00:44:28,233 --> 00:44:29,754
This is all I have.

630
00:44:29,754 --> 00:44:32,007
Only for you.

631
00:44:37,391 --> 00:44:39,990
How was it? Are you full?

632
00:44:39,990 --> 00:44:41,470
Can you eat this type of food?

633
00:44:41,470 --> 00:44:43,280
Yes, I can.

634
00:44:45,238 --> 00:44:46,814
Are you sure?

635
00:44:46,814 --> 00:44:49,207
You were so funny.

636
00:44:49,207 --> 00:44:52,647
I noticed you couldn't get in line.

637
00:44:54,238 --> 00:44:55,948
You're really good at it.

638
00:44:55,948 --> 00:44:58,424
So many people, but you still got through.

639
00:44:58,424 --> 00:44:59,866
I'm not good.

640
00:44:59,867 --> 00:45:01,603
I should be the one to ask.

641
00:45:01,603 --> 00:45:04,733
Why don't you know how to buy food from the canteen?

642
00:45:09,870 --> 00:45:11,868
You don't have to frown like that.

643
00:45:11,868 --> 00:45:14,338
I'm not scolding you or anything.

644
00:45:15,648 --> 00:45:18,181
I know you're a kind person.

645
00:45:18,181 --> 00:45:20,324
