646
00:45:20,844 --> 00:45:22,764
The shuttle bus is here.

647
00:45:26,298 --> 00:45:27,978
Aren't you coming?

648
00:45:28,714 --> 00:45:32,294
Don't tell me you've never used the shuttle bus.

649
00:45:32,294 --> 00:45:34,167
Never.

650
00:45:34,167 --> 00:45:36,566
You're such a Koon-Chai.

651
00:45:45,490 --> 00:45:48,278
Hey, Ae! Where are you going?

652
00:45:48,279 --> 00:45:50,101
Wait for me!

653
